<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Concerning SVN standard/incubator:</p>

<p>The problem occured when requesting manifest data for a custom method listing</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$searchParams = array(
            'name'  =&gt; 'cliProviderName',
            'type'  =&gt; 'Provider',
            'value' =&gt; 'some-class',
);

//...

$searchParams = array(
           'name'                 =&gt; 'cliActionableMethodLongParameters',
            'type'                  =&gt; 'Provider',
            'providerName'  =&gt;    'SomeClass'
            'actionName'    =&gt;     'Action',
            'specialtyName' =&gt;    '_Default',
);
</code></pre>

<p>Changing the providerName did return null in both cases.</p>

